posting_body: ['11100 Southeast Petrovitsky Road, Renton, WA 98055', 'At Benson Downs, every spacious\xa0one-, two- and three-bedroom floor plan has been thoughtfully designed to complement your personal style of living.', '\xa0 Our\xa0apartment features include private balconies / patios, cozy fireplaces, large living areas and full-size washers and dryers.', 'Our controlled access community is set amongst beautiful greenery and our amenities include after-hours courtesy patrol and a business center.', 'We are just a 10 minute drive to Boeing and 16 minutes to Seattle-Tacoma International Airport.', 'Community Features:', 'Resident Events', 'Walk-In Closet', 'On-site Recycling', 'Controlled Access', 'Breakfast Bar', 'Controlled Building Access', 'Window Coverings', 'Mass Transit Nearby', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'renton apartments, apartments for rent in renton wa, renton wa apartments, fairwood apartments renton, fairwood apartments renton wa', '*Floor plans and pricing are subject to error, change or deletion.', 'Some photos are for representation purposes only.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
